<i>adjective</i>: 아무렇다 [아ː무러타] <i>adverb</i>: 암만 [암만], 아무리 [아ː무리] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>아무렇다 [아ː무러타]</dt><br>
<dd>1. whatever</dd><br>
<dd>구체적으로 정하지 않은 어떤 상태나 조건에 놓여 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being in a state or condition that is not definite.</dd><br>
<dd>2. careless</dd><br>
<dd>되는대로 막 하는 상태에 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being in a state where one does something without giving much thought to it.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>암만 [암만]</dt><br>
<dd>1. no matter how</dd><br>
<dd>정도가 매우 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>To an extremely severe degree.</dd><br>
<dd>2. no matter how; however; whatever</dd><br>
<dd>비록 그렇다 하더라도.</dd><br>
<dd>Even so.</dd><br>
<dt>아무리 [아ː무리]</dt><br>
<dd>1. no matter how</dd><br>
<dd>정도가 매우 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>To an extremely severe degree.</dd><br>
<dd>2. no matter how; however; whatever</dd><br>
<dd>비록 그렇다 하더라도.</dd><br>
<dd>Even so.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>